00:52:51,440 --> 00:52:53,954
I knew I was scared
of Andre Junior.

722
00:52:54,160 --> 00:52:55,832
Like father, like son.

723
00:52:56,040 --> 00:52:59,112
The guava doesn't fall
too far from the tree.

724
00:52:59,320 --> 00:53:00,639
He was also a cannibal.

725
00:53:00,840 --> 00:53:03,957
They say he would eat
a victim's heart while it was beating,

726
00:53:04,160 --> 00:53:06,310
to give him superhuman strength.

727
00:53:06,520 --> 00:53:09,318
[gunfire]

728
00:53:13,040 --> 00:53:16,271
Monrovia itself
was like being on another planet.

729
00:53:16,480 --> 00:53:18,198
Planet Monrovia.

730
00:53:18,400 --> 00:53:22,598
From the temperature, it was obviously
a planet close to the sun.

731
00:53:22,800 --> 00:53:26,031
I rarely saw another white man,
and I never left town alone.

732
00:53:26,240 --> 00:53:30,392
Outside town was the edge of hell.
I didn't wanna even gaze into it.

733
00:53:30,600 --> 00:53:35,071
[Andre Jr] This is your hotel.
Two stars.

734
00:53:36,120 --> 00:53:38,076
Can you bring me the gun of Rambo?

735
00:53:38,280 --> 00:53:41,556
- Part one, two or three?
- I've only seen part one.

736
00:53:41,760 --> 00:53:44,638
The M-60. Would you like
the armour-piercing bullets?

737
00:53:44,840 --> 00:53:46,114
Please.

738
00:53:47,440 --> 00:53:50,750
My father left a welcoming present
in your room.

739
00:53:50,960 --> 00:53:52,598
Enjoy. [laughs]

740
00:54:01,480 --> 00:54:03,436
[distant gunfire]

741
00:54:04,440 --> 00:54:06,158
[French]

742
00:54:06,360 --> 00:54:10,592
My God.
She nearly got her head cut off.

